&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reference No.  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;J127-A-20-0620&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours: 37.5 hours per week &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Base: Siskin Dental Centre, Norwich Community Hospital,&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Bowthorpe Road, Norwich, NR2 3TU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary: £64,970 - £75,991 per annum &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt; &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Do you want to make a real difference in a socially minded, values driven organisation? &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Do you want to work where your voice can be heard?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are an award-winning employee owned social enterprise, providing high quality community dental services across east and central England.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited from enthusiastic dentists for the post of Senior Dental Officer based at the Siskin Dental Centre in Norwich.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will deliver dental care and advice to patients and their carers from community groups including patients with additional needs, who are clients of Community Dental Services. Services to be provided include preventive care and advice, dental treatment, care under sedation and general anaesthesia, and epidemiological field work.Working at other locations to support the client group will be required including other clinics, domiciliary and hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Community Dental Services encourages postgraduate education and development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please do not hesitate contact Angela Simms, Clinical Lead, to discuss the roles available or to arrange visits to the clinics on 07879 668955, angela.simms@cds-cic.co.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date: 19th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview Date: To be arranged&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you wish to make an application, please apply via NHS Jobs.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
